Articles.Content:
Is it just me or are the RoveMax M1 wheels indestructible?  I'm using v1.1.2 and no matter how hard I try I can't burst them. I dropped rovers from great heights, shattered the rovers, but the wheels remain intact. The TR-2L on the other hand I can break with ease.

Update: ok it took a lot of work but I managed to burst one, none the less they are ridiculously stronger then the TR-2L

Edited May 10, 2016 by RuBisCO
